  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is structurally complete and plausible; however, it declares signatureAlg ed25519 and provides a valid hash but omits the actual signature value, rendering structural integrity unverifiable (W-SI-01).",
