      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R1) has vendor-supplied QA documentation, but site-specific validation of the hemolysis user-defined function (UDF) was performed only informally. No regression test suite covers the UDF. Achieved level 2; required level 4 for MRL 5."
