    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps identified at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package for submission on the basis that Monte Carlo UQ bounds remain below the absolute clinical hemolysis threshold at the 95th percentile across all five operating points. The decision acknowledges that six factors remain unassessed and seven assessed factors fall below required levels; a risk-informed acceptance was granted contingent on post-market surveillance. NOTE: This package declares signatureAlg ed25519 and provides a content hash but the signature value is absent, meaning the hash-to-content binding cannot be cryptographically verified.",
